### Get your tickets here:

👉 [Peatix](https://zigday.peatix.com/)


Our goal is to bring together developers, makers, and newcomers alike to share projects, experiments, tools, and stories. Whether you write games, build systems tools, or are just curious about programming for the first time, you’re warmly welcome here. Expect a day with maybe lightning talks, live demos, and chances to connect and collaborate with systems programmers, creative coders, and beginners who want to learn together.


🌏 Language: English + Japanese friendly (presentations encouraged in English if possible)

🧩 Topics we love: game development, low-level programming, compilers, tools, creative coding, embedded systems, and open-source culture

💡 Spirit: collaborative, experimental, and open — everyone’s welcome.

🪶 Interested in giving a short talk or lightning presentation?

### Register here:
👉 [Speaker Application](https://secretshop.osaka/en/zigday-apply/)

<sub><sup>Accepted speakers will receive a free event pass.</sup></sub>
<sub><sup> We’ll get back to you soon! </sup></sub>

